    },
    {
      "id": "1a76adc5_8b621815",
      "file_path": "vid-app-common/src/main/java/org/onap/vid/dao/FnAppDbConnection.java",
      "patchset_number": 9,
      "line": 13,
      "message": "I'd recommend using guava preconditions for these null checks and just failing in case null values arrive here. Less branched code and quick termination of the flow and avoiding a potential NPE by relying on a null-referenced Connection.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 2815,
        "name": "Michal Kabaj",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "michal.kabaj@nokia.com",
        "username": "kabayashi"
      },
      "updated": "2018-09-25 18:07:33.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "id": "1a76adc5_8b9458e9",
      "file_path": "vid-app-common/src/main/java/org/onap/vid/dao/FnAppDoaImpl.java",
      "patchset_number": 9,
      "line": 41,
      "message": "The method declares SQLException is thrown, while the implementation rethrows a Exception. A good practice is to catch and rethrow a more specific exception. In this case SQLException.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 2815,
        "name": "Michal Kabaj",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "michal.kabaj@nokia.com",
        "username": "kabayashi"
      },
      "updated": "2018-09-25 18:07:33.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "id": "1a76adc5_ebf70c58",
      "file_path": "vid-app-common/src/main/java/org/onap/vid/dao/FnAppDoaImpl.java",
      "patchset_number": 9,
      "line": 44,
      "message": "Would it be possible to reduce the number of nested try clauses to just one ? try-with-resources allows to have several resources opened in one try()",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 2815,
        "name": "Michal Kabaj",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "michal.kabaj@nokia.com",
        "username": "kabayashi"
      },
      "updated": "2018-09-25 18:07:33.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "id": "1a76adc5_0bda88e9",
      "file_path": "vid-app-common/src/main/java/org/onap/vid/dao/FnAppDoaImpl.java",
      "patchset_number": 9,
      "line": 52,
      "message": "What is the point of doing a rollback when no transaction is ever opened and committed ? The query is a simple select which does not do any updates on the DB. So the rollback is redundant :)",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 2815,
        "name": "Michal Kabaj",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "michal.kabaj@nokia.com",
        "username": "kabayashi"
      },
      "updated": "2018-09-25 18:07:33.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "id": "1a76adc5_e66743b6",
      "file_path": "vid-app-common/src/test/java/org/onap/vid/controllers/HealthCheckControllerTest.java",
      "patchset_number": 9,
      "line": 28,
      "message": "Please reorder the field declarations. constants first :)",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 2815,
        "name": "Michal Kabaj",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "michal.kabaj@nokia.com",
